column2: SELECT TOP #  S.ObjID, S.z,  &&&, L.ew, L.ewErr,  &&&, L2.ew ,L2.ewErr  &&&,L3.ew,L3.ewErr FROM SpecPhoto AS S   JOIN SpecLine AS L ON S.SpecObjID = L.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecLine AS L2 ON S.SpecObjID = L2.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecLine AS L3 ON S.SpecObjID = L3.SpecObjID  WHERE  L.LineId = #  and L2.LineId = #  and L3.LineID = # and (specclass=# or specclass=#) and S.zconf > .# and S.z < #
